snippet.title: Yuki no Wai Wai Kids 3/16 | 有紀のワイワイキッズ 3/16
snippet.description:
Finally decided to try recording this for Youtube.

This video shows a game that appears similar to "WaiWai Check", but with a competitive twist featuring an AI that not only is difficult, but blatantly cheats.

And the "Yuki" in this one? Yuki Uchida. Huh.

As far as I've managed, only bsnes-based emulators can boot this. I'd recommend LuigiBlood's bsnes-sx;

http://bsxproj.superfamicom.org/

More info coming soon:
http://superfamicom.org/blog
